source.name: Country Specific Information
source.description: Country Specific Information is available for every country of the world. It includes such information as location of the U.S. embassy or consulate in the subject country, unusual immigration practices, health conditions, minor political disturbances, unusual currency and entry regulations, crime and security information, and drug penalties
